ANTHRAX, BOVINE - SLOVENIA (02): (NORTH EAST) NOT
*************************************************

A ProMED-mail post
http://www.promedmail.org
ProMED-mail is a program of the
International Society for Infectious Diseases
http://www.isid.org

Date: Thu 8 Sep 2011
Source: RTV SLO [in Slovenian, trans., edited]
http://www.rtvslo.si/okolje/govedo-ni-bilo-okuzeno-z-vranicnim-prisadom/265829


Cattle not infected with anthrax; all measures therefore terminated
-------------------------------------------------------------------
Additional diagnostic tests in the laboratory rebutted the suspicion
of anthrax, which a practicing veterinarian diagnosed on Monday [5 Sep
2011] of the cattle in the municipality of Vitanje.

The Veterinary Administration shall be notified that the prescribed
measures be terminated in regard to the cattle on the farm.

--
Communicated by:
Sabine Zentis
Castleview Pedigree English Longhorns
Gut Laach
